edu.harvard.integer.service.managementobject.snmp

Interface MibLoaderLocalInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MibLoader

    public interface MibLoaderLocalInterface
    Manager used to load a parsed MIB into the database.

    NOTE: The is a helper manager to the MibService. This is always run locally to the MibService that is importing a MIB.
